Kurt McKinney https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kurt_McKinney 0 Kurt Robin McKinney (born February 15, 1962 in Louisville, Kentucky) is an American actor. McKinney is perhaps best known for his role as Jason Stillwell in 1986 martial arts film No Retreat, No Surrender.
